Summary of changes relative to upstream SLIPS:
    - Added an OT/ICS (Operational Technology) detection module:
      modules/ot_detection/
    - Added OT-protocol Zeek scripts: zeek-scripts/ot_protocols.zeek
      (Modbus, DNP3, S7Comm / industrial protocol analysis).
    - Added OT configuration: config/ot_protected_devices.conf,
      config/modbus_authorized_masters.conf, and the `ot_detection`
      section of config/smartshield.yaml.
    - Tuned detection thresholds and analysis direction for industrial /
      factory deployments.
    - Rebranded the user-facing product name from SLIPS to SmartShield.

See the README section "Our contributions vs. upstream" for detail.
